Broderick Stephen `` Steve '' Harvey -LRB- born January 17 , 1957 -RRB- is an American comedian , television host , producer , radio personality , actor , and author .
He hosts The Steve Harvey Morning Show , the Steve Harvey talk show , Family Feud and Little Big Shots .
He is the author of Act Like a Lady , Think Like a Man , which was published in March 2009 , and the book Straight Talk , No Chaser : How to Find and Keep a Man .
Harvey previously hosted Showtime at the Apollo , starred in The Steve Harvey Show , and was featured in The Original Kings of Comedy .
He is a five-time Daytime Emmy Award winner , and a 14-time NAACP Image Award winner in various categories .